Package: svgPanZoom
Title: Add pan and zoom to almost any R graphic
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Anders", "Riutta et. al.", role = c("aut", "cph"),
    comment = "svg-pan-zoom.js library in htmlwidgets/lib,
    https://github.com/ariutta/svg-pan-zoom"),
    person("Kent", "Russell", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = "R interface to svg-pan-zoom.js", email =
    "kent.russell@timelyportfolio.com")
    )
Description: svgPanZoom is an htmlwidget that provides pan and zoom
    interactivity to R graphics, including base, lattice, and ggplot2.  The
    interactivity is provided through the svg-pan-zoom.js library.  Various
    options to the widget can tailor the pan + zoom experience to nearly any
    user desire.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.2)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
Suggests:
    gridSVG,
    htmltools,
    knitr,
    SVGAnnotation,
VignetteBuilder: knitr
